{
  "stem": "27340.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we could hardly, hardly move around, in order to at least provide for the next six or 12 or 18 months of clothes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And nobody knew who was going to take care of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were we going to go into a camp?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Were we going to go into a family?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Were we going to be in a hostel, whatever happened?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The main thing was out of Germany and into safety.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On our transport, possibly from Breslau, there may have been about 20.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We then spent the night in Berlin, where other transports of that nature were being organized.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I suppose on our trip, ultimately in England, there must have been about 150, 160 who arrived there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Um, not as far as I know, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Certainly not those outside Breslau, and from Breslau itself, I don't recall anybody, no, no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And perhaps one of the sad things was to leave one's own friends behind, who perhaps matter at the moment more than one's parents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Peers have a tremendous influence on people, especially when they're young.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Up to the age of 30, 35 or so, I think, that- that- that plays a very important part, and certainly played an important part to us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very unfortunate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As we came to the Dutch border, the German passport control came in, the customs people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were, of course, all Nazis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And they didn't look at every suitcase, but they certainly picked-- and we were about eight or 10 in the compartment in the group-- th-- they picked my brother's suitcase.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had to get this out of the luggage rack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had to open it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When I, as I released the lock, of course, the, the, the lid spraying out.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
